&lt;li&gt;Ensure document control practices meet internal governance, client expectations, and applicable GxP / computerized systems requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain version control, approvals, archival, training linkage, and retention controls for quality records.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
