&lt;p&gt;The Operations Project Manager will support the operation of the AI Governance Council (AIGC) and Enterprise PMO (ePMO) governance/support activities. This role is responsible for coordinating AI governance processes, managing AI use case intake and tracking, facilitating governance reviews, maintaining governance documentation, and supporting operations project management needs. Reports to the Operations Program Manager responsible for execution and operational oversight.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is ideal for a highly organized, analytical professional interested in project management, governance, AI enablement, operational excellence, and enterprise transformation.&lt;/p&gt;
