&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and facilitate AI Governance Council (AIGC) meetings and review sessions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage AI use case intake, governance workflows, and submission tracking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review AI use case submissions for completeness and readiness prior to governance review.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate stakeholder reviews across Technology, Security, Legal, Compliance, Risk, and Business teams.&lt;/li&gt;
